### Phase 8: Monitoring and Validation

**14. Container Health Monitoring**
Advanced health check systems:
```nix
Healthcheck = {
  Test = [ "CMD" "curl" "-f" "http://localhost:4000/health" ];
  Interval = 30000000000;  # 30 seconds
  Timeout = 10000000000;   # 10 seconds
  Retries = 3;
};
```

**15. Container Readiness Monitoring**
Sophisticated readiness monitoring with `monitor_container_readiness.exs`:
- Real-time container status tracking
- Initialization progress monitoring
- Service availability validation
